{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#12425: the issue of reactivity on multiple select",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:21:43.881696+00:00",
  "text": "the issue of reactivity on multiple select\n\n### Vue version\n\n3.5.12\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\n\nhttps://play.vuejs.org/#\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nselect multiple options\r\n![CleanShot 2024-11-18 at 15 54 41@2x](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/6a31d206-5d75-40e1-994d-d8922f1b358a)\r\n\r\n\n\n### What is expected?\n\nit should select the first one, but multiple options were selected\r\n\r\n![CleanShot 2024-11-18 at 15 55 05@2x](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/34e5933d-4b20-4ded-a5a8-af525be7bb1f)\r\n\n\n### What is actually happening?\n\nit seems working on vue2, but not on vue3\n\n### System Info\n\n_No response_\n\n### Any additional comments?\n\nnot sure it was expected or not.\r\n\r\nif it's expected, what's the right way for it?",
  "language": "en",
